{
  "stem": "13874.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I talked to him, and we complained bitterly about our fate, which it wasn't anything of pleasure.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, what are you talking about?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You are here for six weeks, three months.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I have been here for four weeks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "From those who came six weeks ago, 1/2 of them are already released.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I have not a chance of getting out of here alive, but I am sure my brother-in-law will see to it that he will never see me.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So what-- so it was not only the Jews who suffered.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he told us a little bit about the history of Dachau.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Dachau, as I mentioned before, was founded in 1933, right away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in 1936, it was rebuilt for the primary purpose of taking care of the falloff from the Reichstag.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And from 1936 till 1938, to the Kristallnacht, there were no Jews in Dachau.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were all political prisoners-- Germans-- fellow Germans.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so it wasn't only the Jews who suffered.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Yes, I know there was latent anti-- anti-Semitism in Germany.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was all over Europe.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's all over the world Yes, I know Hitler got into power with a majority of votes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But in order for Hitler to do what he wanted to do, a majority wasn't good enough.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He had to get total support, total allegiance, and everybody had to march in the same step.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that is primarily what the concentration camps were for, and were used for that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were just a-- a byproduct.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And one of the biggest crimes in Germany was-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] This-- this crazy-- [NON-ENGLISH]-- disparaging-- it's a kind of-- it was a political crime punished-- punishable by a concentration camp, which was outside the regular jurisdiction of the German government.",
      "word_count": 43
    }
  ],
